Title 2 - ADMINISTRATION AND PERSONNEL,Chapter 2.18 - CALAVERAS COUNTY CHILDREN AND FAMILIES COMMISSION,2.18.010 - Purpose.,"Calaveras_County | Title 2 - ADMINISTRATION AND PERSONNEL | Chapter 2.18 - CALAVERAS COUNTY CHILDREN AND FAMILIES COMMISSION | 2.18.010 - Purpose.
The Calaveras County Children and Families Commission shall comply with all provisions, amendments, requirements and revisions of California Health and Safety Code Section 130100 through 130158 governing First 5 commissions, to ensure compliance with federal, state and locally legislated mandates, revisions and operational requirements. (Ord. No. 3095, § 3, 2-27-2018) ",Calaveras_County,20,Calaveras_County.pdf,80
