Title 2 - ADMINISTRATION AND PERSONNEL,Chapter 2.32 - SEPARATION OR CONSOLIDATION OF CERTAIN OFFICES,"2.32.030 - Separation of combined o␀ce of clerk, auditor and controller.","Calaveras_County | Title 2 - ADMINISTRATION AND PERSONNEL | Chapter 2.32 - SEPARATION OR CONSOLIDATION OF CERTAIN OFFICES | 2.32.030 - Separation of combined o␀ce of clerk, auditor and controller.
A. There is created the separate elective office of county auditor, and the duties of this office shall be those as set forth by law and specifically Section 26900 et seq. of the Government Code of the state. B. The office of county clerk and county recorder shall remain combined, and the duties of said office shall remain those as set forth by law, and specifically as to the county clerk, those duties as set forth in Section 26800 et seq. of the Government Code of the state, and, specifically as to the county recorder, those as set forth by Section 27200 et seq. of the Government Code of the state. (Ord. 526 § 1, 1969). Cross reference— For further provisions on the offices of auditor and controller, see hapter 2.24 of this code. ",Calaveras_County,26,Calaveras_County.pdf,170
Title 2 - ADMINISTRATION AND PERSONNEL,Chapter 2.32 - SEPARATION OR CONSOLIDATION OF CERTAIN OFFICES,2.32.040 - Combined o␀ces of clerk and recorder and of auditor and controller established.,"Calaveras_County | Title 2 - ADMINISTRATION AND PERSONNEL | Chapter 2.32 - SEPARATION OR CONSOLIDATION OF CERTAIN OFFICES | 2.32.040 - Combined o␀ces of clerk and recorder and of auditor and controller established.
Upon the expiration of the term of the holder of the combined office of county clerk, auditor and recorder at the time of the effective date of the ordinance codified in this section, or upon his death or resignation, whichever event first occurs, then the combined office of county clerk and recorder is established, and the combined office of county auditor and county controller is established. (Ord. 526 § 6, 1969). Cross reference— For further provisions on the offices of auditor and controller, see hapter 2.24 of this code. ",Calaveras_County,26,Calaveras_County.pdf,112
