Title 3 - REVENUE AND FINANCE,Chapter 3.40 - PROCEDURE FOR LEASING COUNTY REALTY,3.40.010 - Authority.,"Calaveras_County | Title 3 - REVENUE AND FINANCE | Chapter 3.40 - PROCEDURE FOR LEASING COUNTY REALTY | 3.40.010 - Authority.
This chapter is adopted pursuant to Government Code Section 25537. The procedures established by this chapter are supplemental to procedures established by state law for the leasing of county-owned property. Failure to follow the procedures set forth in this chapter shall not invalidate any lease which otherwise has been entered in compliance with law. (Ord. 1844 § 9(part), 1986). ",Calaveras_County,111,Calaveras_County.pdf,76
Title 3 - REVENUE AND FINANCE,Chapter 3.40 - PROCEDURE FOR LEASING COUNTY REALTY,3.40.020 - Call for bids.,"Calaveras_County | Title 3 - REVENUE AND FINANCE | Chapter 3.40 - PROCEDURE FOR LEASING COUNTY REALTY | 3.40.020 - Call for bids.
