Title 3 - REVENUE AND FINANCE,Chapter 3.54 - CHARGES REASONABLY NECESSARY TO RECOVER COSTS OF PROVIDING COPIES UNDER THE PUBLIC RECORDS ACT,3.54.050 - Board of supervisors may waive weighted salary charges.,"Calaveras_County | Title 3 - REVENUE AND FINANCE | Chapter 3.54 - CHARGES REASONABLY NECESSARY TO RECOVER COSTS OF PROVIDING COPIES UNDER THE PUBLIC RECORDS ACT | 3.54.050 - Board of supervisors may waive weighted salary charges.
