This chapter shall be known as the ""Commercial Cannabis Activity Tax Ordinance."" This chapter shall be applicable in the unincorporated area of the county of Calaveras, the county of Calaveras will be referred to as ""county."" (Measure G, § 1, 11-3-2020) ",Calaveras_County,123,Calaveras_County.pdf,66
