The ordinance codified in this chapter establishes and prescribes measures for the regulation of ambulance services within the county. It shall be known as the ""Ambulance Ordinance of Calaveras County."" (Ord. 2866 (part), 2005). ",Calaveras_County,178,Calaveras_County.pdf,53
