Title 6 - ANIMALS,Chapter 6.10 - CONTROL AND NUISANCES,"6.10.080 - Stallions, bulls, boars, rams and male goats.","Calaveras_County | Title 6 - ANIMALS | Chapter 6.10 - CONTROL AND NUISANCES | 6.10.080 - Stallions, bulls, boars, rams and male goats.
