Title 6 - ANIMALS,Chapter 6.10 - CONTROL AND NUISANCES,6.10.100 - Retention without owner's consent.,"Calaveras_County | Title 6 - ANIMALS | Chapter 6.10 - CONTROL AND NUISANCES | 6.10.100 - Retention without owner's consent.
