A. The county's code compliance unit shall enforce violations of this chapter pursuant to the provisions of Chapter 8.06 of the county code. (Ord. No. 3175, § 1, 10-11-2022; Ord. No. 3189, § 1, 12-12-2023) ",Calaveras_County,385,Calaveras_County.pdf,71
