Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.020 - Advisory agency.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.020 - Advisory agency.
""Advisory agency"" means the county planning department. The advisory agency is charged with the responsibility of making investigations, recommendations and reports on the design and improvement of all subdivisions, and has the authority to recommend what actions shall be taken on projects governed by this title. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,498,Calaveras_County.pdf,70
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.030 - Appeal board.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.030 - Appeal board.
""Appeal board"" means the board of supervisors. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,498,Calaveras_County.pdf,27
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.040 - Applicant.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.040 - Applicant.
""Applicant"" means that person or entity proposing, and making application to, subdivide land pursuant to the Subdivision Map Act and Title 16 of the Calaveras County Code. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,498,Calaveras_County.pdf,54
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.050 - Board.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.050 - Board.
""Board"" means the county board of supervisors. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,498,Calaveras_County.pdf,26
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.060 - Building o␀cial.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.060 - Building o␀cial.
""Building official"" means the county building official and head of the building department or his authorized representative. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,498,Calaveras_County.pdf,36
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.070 - Development.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.070 - Development.
""Development"" means the uses to which the land which is the subject of a map shall be put, the buildings to be constructed upon it, and all alterations of the land and construction incident thereto. (Ord. 1820 § 2(part), 1986). ",Calaveras_County,498,Calaveras_County.pdf,57
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.080 - Completed application.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.080 - Completed application.
An application will be deemed complete upon the submittal of a completed application form, requisite fees, a tentative map, and such other information and material as may be required by the planning department, this title, and the Map Act. An application shall not be deemed complete until the planning director so determines. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,498,Calaveras_County.pdf,77
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.090 - Director of environmental health.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.090 - Director of environmental health.
""Director of environmental health"" means the director of the Calaveras County environmental health department, or the director's designee. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,498,Calaveras_County.pdf,42
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.100 - Director of public works.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.100 - Director of public works.
""Director of public works"" shall mean the county director of public works or his authorized representative. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,499,Calaveras_County.pdf,35
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.120 - Engineer.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.120 - Engineer.
""Engineer"" means a civil engineer registered in the state of California as defined in Section 6731 of the Business and Professions Code. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,499,Calaveras_County.pdf,45
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.130 - Environmental health department.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.130 - Environmental health department.
""Environmental health department"" means the Calaveras County environmental health department. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,499,Calaveras_County.pdf,31
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.160 - Gift deed.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.160 - Gift deed.
""Gift deed"" means the conveyance of real property title to a parcel or lot, including the creation of a new parcel or lot, where the grantor receives no consideration for the grant, title or deed. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,499,Calaveras_County.pdf,59
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.165 - Ground water.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.165 - Ground water.
""Ground water"" means that part of the subsurface water which is in the zone of saturation as defined in Chapter 8.20. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,499,Calaveras_County.pdf,44
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.170 - Ground water map.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.170 - Ground water map.
""Ground water map"" means the map adopted by the county depicting geology and ground water availability. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,499,Calaveras_County.pdf,36
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.175 - Ground water zone.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.175 - Ground water zone.
""Ground water zone"" means those areas depicted on the ground water map that demonstrate ground water potential. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,499,Calaveras_County.pdf,36
