Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.260 - Map.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.260 - Map.
""Map"" means one of the following: A. ""Tentative"" means a map prepared from existing field records and data in sufficient detail to meet the requirements of this title. B. ""Final"" means a map prepared in accordance with this title, the Map Act, Land Surveyors Act, and the tentative map. C. ""Parcel"" means a map prepared in accordance with this title, the Map Act, Land Surveyors Act and the tentative map. D. ""Record of survey"" means a map prepared in accordance with the provisions of the Land Surveyors Act to delineate land boundaries, property lines, or other lines or points of a survey. E. ""Reversion to acreage"" means a map prepared in accordance with this title, the Map Act, and Land Surveyors Act for the purposes of reverting previously divided parcels to acreage. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,500,Calaveras_County.pdf,191
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.270 - Map Act.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.270 - Map Act.
(§ 66410) The ""Map Act"" refers to the California Subdivision Map Act, Title 7, Division 2, commencing with Section 66410 of the Government Code. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,500,Calaveras_County.pdf,56
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.300 - Owner.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.300 - Owner.
