Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.330 - Planning agency.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.330 - Planning agency.
""Planning agency"" means the county planning department. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,501,Calaveras_County.pdf,26
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.340 - Planning commission.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.340 - Planning commission.
""Planning commission"" or ""commission"" means the county planning commission. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,501,Calaveras_County.pdf,30
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.350 - Planning director.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.350 - Planning director.
""Planning director"" means the county planning director or his authorized representative. (Ord. 1523 § 1(part), 1982). ",Calaveras_County,501,Calaveras_County.pdf,30
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.355 - Potable water.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.355 - Potable water.
""Potable water"" means, for the purposes of this chapter, water that meets bacteriological and nitrate standards equal to that of a transient noncommunity water system pursuant to the California Safe Drinking Water Act. Additional analyses, including general mineral analyses, may be required when deemed necessary and at the discretion of the director. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,501,Calaveras_County.pdf,80
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.356 - Proof of ground water.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.356 - Proof of ground water.
""Proof of ground water"" means the demonstration of an adequate water supply pursuant to Chapter 16.12. (Ord. 2590 § 1(part), 1999). ",Calaveras_County,501,Calaveras_County.pdf,38
Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS,16.03.360 - Public works.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.03 - DEFINITIONS | 16.03.360 - Public works.
