Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS,Chapter 16.11 - SUBDIVISION ROAD STANDARDS,16.11.030 - Minimum service roads and two parcel subdivisions.,"Calaveras_County | Title 16 - SUBDIVISIONS | Chapter 16.11 - SUBDIVISION ROAD STANDARDS | 16.11.030 - Minimum service roads and two parcel subdivisions.
