This chapter establishes a process for review and approval of uses that are intended to be of limited duration of time and will not permanently alter the character or physical facilities of the site where they occur. ",Calaveras_County,725,Calaveras_County.pdf,39
Title 17 - ZONING,Chapter 17.32 - Temporary Use Permits,17.32.020 - Applicability.,"Calaveras_County | Title 17 - ZONING | Chapter 17.32 - Temporary Use Permits | 17.32.020 - Applicability.
