Title 17 - ZONING,Chapter 17.40 - Speci␀c Plans,17.40.010 - Purpose.,"Calaveras_County | Title 17 - ZONING | Chapter 17.40 - Speci␀c Plans | 17.40.010 - Purpose.
The purpose of this chapter is to establish a process for preparing, processing, reviewing, adopting, and amending specific plans in compliance with Government Code Section 65450 et seq., or as that Section may be amended or replaced from time to time. The purpose of a specific plan is to systematically implement the general plan in particularly designated areas. ",Calaveras_County,739,Calaveras_County.pdf,69
