The planning commission shall act as the advisory body for all specific plans and provide recommendations to the Board of Supervisors. The board of supervisors shall act as the review authority, and after receiving recommendations from the Planning Commission, may adopt, reject, or modify all Specific Plans. ",Calaveras_County,739,Calaveras_County.pdf,55
Title 17 - ZONING,Chapter 17.40 - Speci␀c Plans,17.40.040 - Initiation.,"Calaveras_County | Title 17 - ZONING | Chapter 17.40 - Speci␀c Plans | 17.40.040 - Initiation.
